d":210499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"6c82fb397e6dbabdb856a4440c173f0e98f865d6","tid":1539714,"uid":2429,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cW2VPf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcW2VPf0.jpg&h=aa42bde4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東語錄：<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n「凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。」<br />\n〈和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話〉，1939年9月16日"},{"pid":"b9fa7a2ea8593416e0acbd123a56ee50726fdc95","tid":1539714,"uid":210499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"b214b3ff2a2e19e680276a56683205501b292bb8","tid":1539714,"uid":271056,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"d07d58b47c30e1d9a5b734f8e9a1570291d3050c","tid":1539714,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831太子站打死人事件後撤回</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKjEwsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKjEwsz.jpg&h=842a8ba1&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地就噉俾個八婆講廢話shift咗focus對唔對得住良心？</span></span>"},{"pid":"738e756fa129d4ca6cd22c0f82648398dcf0bc5d","tid":1539714,"uid":210499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c82fb397e6dbabdb856a4440c173f0e98f865d6","tid":1539714,"uid":2429,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cW2VPf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcW